vicinity /vɪˈsɪnɪtɪ/

1. N-SING If something is in the vicinity of a particular place, it is near it. (在…) 附近 [正式] 

例： There were a hundred or so hotels in the vicinity of the station. 在车站附近有大约一百家左右的旅馆。

